fields.descriptive_line: Set of 60 Ganjifa playing cards with scenes from the Ramayana. By Raghupathi Bhat, Karnataka, India, 1992-3.

fields.name: The Ramayana: Love and Valour in India's Great Epic

fields.physical_description:
Set of 60 ganjifa cards depicting the Ramayana.
List of subjects of the cards (supplied by Raghupathi Bhat):
1. Brahma inspires Valmiki to write the Ramayana.
2. Putrakameshti Yaga, Dasharatha, Vasishta, Prajapathi , Maya, Rishyashrunga.
3. Rama, Lakshmana with Vishvamitra proceeding to the forest.
4. Rama kills Thataki.
5. Vishvamitra preaches to Rama, Lakshmana and giving Astra (they appear in human form).
6. Models of Vishvamitra, Rama and Lakshmana.
7. Liberation of Ahalya from curse (Ahalya, Rama, Lakshmana, Vishvamitra).
8. Seetha Swayamvara. Rama breaks the Bow of Shiva to marry Seetha.
9. Parashurama stops Sri Rama.
10. Seetha-Rama.
11. Kaikeyi ill-advised by Manthara.
12. Rama, Seetha and Lakshmana go to live in the forest.
13. Meeting with Guha on the bank of the Ganges (Guha, Rama, Seetha, Lakshmana and residents of other towns).
14. Rishi Bharadwaja's hermitage.
15. Rama, Seetha, Lakshmana build a hut in Chitrakuta.
16. Paduka Pattabhisheka (Bharatha, Shatrugna and others).
17. Sage Athri's blessing (Seetha, Rama, Lakshmana, Athri and Anasuya).
18. Killing of Demon Viradha.
19. Sage Sharabhanga enters fire and becomes God.
20. Meeting with Jatayu.
21. Killing of Thrishira.
22. Killing of Khara.
23. Illusionary deer (Maya Mriga).
24. Ravana comes to Seetha disguised as a Renunciate (Sanyasi).
25. Jatayu obstructs Ravana and fights with him.
26. Rama and Lakshmana cut the arms of Kabandha.
27. Lakshmana - Rama - Hanumantha.
28. Sugreeva, Rama, Lakshmana, Hanuman, Nala, Neela, Jambava and others. Friendship with Sugreeva.
29. War between Vali and Sugreeva. Rama shooting arrow at Vali.
30. Crowning of Sugreeva.
31. Romance of Sugreeva and Rume.
32. Hanumantha taking ring from Sri Rama.
33. Hanumantha and others searching for Seetha.
34. Sampathi narrates Seetha's affair to other vanaras.
35. Hanumantha jumps into the ocean.
36. Mainaka mountain comes in the way of Hanumantha.
37. Killing of Surase by Hanumantha.
38. Hanumantha enters the mouth of Simhike and comes out by piercing his chest. Gods encourage Hanumantha.
39. Battle between Lankini and Hanuman.
40. Hanumantha hands over the ring of Rama to Seetha.
41. Hanumantha kills Kinkaras.
42. Hanumantha kills Jambumali.
43. Hanumantha kills Akshayakumara.
44. Indrajit arrests Hanumantha by a mighty weapon, "Brahmastra".
45. Hanumantha watches the bright aura of Ravana.
46. Hanumantha sets fire to the City of Lanka
47. Hanumantha returns.
48. Rama crwons Vibheeshana as the King of Lanka before conquering Lanka.
49. Constructing a bridge over the ocean.
50. Beginning of the war.
51. Dhumraksha being killed by Hanumantha.
52. Rama kills Kumbhakarna.
53. Ferocity of Lakshmana, the incarnation of Adisesha (primal snake).
54. Indrajeet killed by Lakshmana.
55. Monkeys appear as lions to the demons.
56. Sri Rama kills Ravana.
57. Crowning ceremony of Vibheeshana.
58. Seetha, Rama, Lakshmana and retinue return to Ayodhya in a flower plane named Pushpaka.
59. They visit the hermitage of Rishi Bharadwaja.
60. Crowning of Sri Rama.
